article.description: — Matt Lewis registered 19 points as James Madison defeated Florida Atlantic 79-70 on Tuesday.
article.headline: Lewis scores 19 to carry James Madison past FAU 79-70
article.linkText: Lewis scores 19 to carry James Madison past FAU 79-70
article.story: HARRISONBURG, Va. -- — Matt Lewis registered 19 points as James Madison defeated Florida Atlantic 79-70 on Tuesday. Justin Amadi had 17 points for James Madison (4-4). Julien Wooden added 12 points and Vado Morse had 10 points. Jailyn Ingram had 20 points for the Owls (5-4). Kenan Blackshear added 14 points and Michael Forrest had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
